review_blob: I had Goose Island India Pale Ale off tap paired with well spiced lamb chops. The aroma and taste held up well against the meat. The finish was a little long but was very enjoyable in a meal.
I really enjoyed the aroma, the finish was nice and clean for such a robust hoppyness.
beer_name: Flying Fish HopFish India Pale Ale

review_blob: Would buy again. Holds up nicely with steak and ribs. Spices are up front and pleasant.
